        <item>You can always reset settings to their default states by going to \'Settings -&gt; Advanced -&gt; Reset to Default\'</item>
        <item>Joining the same room repeatedly? Save it as a shortcut on your device for one-tap access by clicking the small button next to \'Join Room\'.</item>
        <item>Each player has different strengths. If one doesn\'t work well with your video format, try another.</item>
        <item>Syncplay Mobile allows you to play media from direct links. However, YouTube is NOT supported, yet.</item>
